data.description: Don't miss this delightful 3-bed, 2-bath home in the popular Riverwalk neighborhood! Convenience abounds with a location that is minutes from a Centennial Trail trailhead, community park access right across the street, Liberty Lake's Orchard Park and Town Center, which features restaurants, walking paths, playground and splash-pad! The interior features stylish new window treatments, all new interior paint and carpeting in the lower level. Newer furnace and A/C will keep you comfortable year round! Step onto the ALL NEW backyard composite deck w/aluminum railing for outdoor enjoyment and peek-a-boo views of the surrounding hills! Upstairs you'll find two spacious bedrooms, a large bathroom, living room and kitchen w/pantry. Lower level includes a spacious family room, laundry room, full bath and the third bedroom. With its prime location, amenities, and recent updates, this Riverwalk home won't last long. Contact your favorite Realtor today to schedule a showing before it's gone!
